    <span class="c1">// …</span></code></pre></figure></p>

<p>Creamos unos cuantos juguetes:</p>

<p><figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-csharp" data-lang="csharp"><span class="kt">var</span> <span class="n">buzzLightyear</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="k">new</span> <span class="n">Toy</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="n">Name</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="err">“</span><span class="n">Buzz</span><span class="err">”</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Price</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="m">20</span> <span class="p">};</span>
